# LiteERP — Database sau clone / pull

## Muc tieu

Nguoi dung **khong can nho** lenh setup. May moi phai co database `demo` giong seed tren Git.

## Khi nao tu dong / AI phai lam

| Tinh huong | Hanh dong |
|------------|-----------|
| User noi **clone, pull, may moi, chua co data, setup project** | Kiem tra `pgdata/PG_VERSION`. Neu **khong co** → chay `setup-database.bat` (tu thu muc goc `odoo/`). |
| `pgdata/` **da co** | **Khong** chay lai setup (tranh xoa du lieu local). Chi nhac chay `backup-database.bat` + push seed neu user muon cap nhat Git. |
| User chua cai Git hooks | Chay **mot lan** `install-githooks.bat` → sau do moi `git pull` tu restore neu thieu `pgdata`. |

## Lenh (thu muc goc project)

```bat
install-githooks.bat    @ REM mot lan / may
setup-database.bat      @ REM pgdata chua co hoac user yeu cau restore
backup-database.bat     @ REM cap nhat database/seed/demo.dump len Git
start_odoo.bat          @ REM Odoo :8069
```

FE: `cd lite-erp-ui && npm run dev` — data mock trong `mockStore.js`, khong can DB.

## File quan trong

- Seed: `database/seed/demo.dump` (tren Git)
- Huong dan: `SETUP.md`
- `pgdata/`, `pgsql.log` — **khong** commit

## Token

Neu chi can xac nhan da co data: kiem tra `pgdata/PG_VERSION` + file seed, khong doc toan bo `pgdata/`.
